Datang.

363
00:21:19,020 --> 00:21:19,860
Tiup padanya.

364
00:21:20,340 --> 00:21:21,540
Anda mengambil masa terlalu lama.

365
00:21:21,540 --> 00:21:23,060
Biar saya buat.

366
