472
00:26:44,300 --> 00:26:45,260
Bulan lalu ini,

473
00:26:45,260 --> 00:26:47,260
Ding Yue dan saya telah bimbang sakit.

474
00:26:48,340 --> 00:26:49,460
Adakah isteri anda di sini?

475
00:26:49,460 --> 00:26:51,340
Dia keluarga kami
"Pesuruhjaya Kesihatan."

476
00:26:51,340 --> 00:26:52,820
Bagaimana dia tidak datang untuk ini?

477
00:26:52,820 --> 00:26:54,170
Dia berada di hospital bersama Songge.

478
00:26:54,700 --> 00:26:55,820
By the way, Ketua Liu,

479
00:26:55,820 --> 00:26:56,700
